r><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 18.0px;"><span style="font-family: microsoft yahei;"><strong>三、评价申诉操作</strong></span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1、<span style="text-indent: 0.0cm;">通过上述方式，找到之前提交过的申请记录，在对应的订单后面点击<b><u>补充凭证</u></b>入口</span></span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><img style="margin: 0.0px;float: none;" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/sns_album/i1/T1FFHTXjhnXXb1upjX.jpg"/></span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2、通过补充凭证入口填入所需信息</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><img style="margin: 0.0px;float: none;" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/sns_album/i4/T1dZnWXfVfXXb1upjX.jpg"/></span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3、申诉提交成功后的处理时间：3-5个工作日</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="font-size: 18.0px;"><span style="font-family: microsoft yahei;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">四、常见问题FAQ</span></strong></span></span></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table><table border="1" bordercolor="#ffffff" width="740"><tbody><tr><td bgcolor="#99ffff" width="50"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>提问</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td width="674"><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><span style="line-height: 15.75pt;margin: 0.0cm 0.0cm 0.0pt;">我都填好了无法提交怎么办？</span></span></span></span></strong></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#ff99ff" rowspan="2"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>回答</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><span style="line-height: 15.75pt;">1.建议检查信息是否按照页面提示要求填写完整，或更换浏览器：推荐使用火狐或谷歌（对浏览器历史记录，cookies等进行一下清理），所有的订单只能提交一次，建议您准备好完整和充足的证据再做提交哦~</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><span style="line-height: 15.75pt;">2.如果提供的订单号，不是提交人作为卖方的订单，提示不能提交（即，账户登陆人必须为卖家大号）</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#99ffff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>提问</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">为什么提交订单页面显示双方未互评不能提交，明明我们是自动回评买家了呀？</span></span></span></strong></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#ff99ff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>回答</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 需要双方互评后才能提交申请，如果是单方评价，在评价期满生效后，也是可以提交的（注：中差评是不会默认回评的，建议您在交易成功后15天内及时主动回评）。</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#99ffff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>提问</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">中差评提交凭证，无法提取举证号，提示对方不是好友、找不到买家账号，或已被对方拉黑等情况如何处理？</span></span></span></strong></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#ff99ff" rowspan="6"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>回答</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这些均不会影响提取举证号信息，请按照如下步骤操作：</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">1).先打开消息管理器</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">2).直接点击右上方的<u>举证按钮</u>，会弹出投诉举证对话框</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">3).在<u>投诉对象</u>中直接输入买家会员，再点击<u>提交证据</u>即可，如图：</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><img style="margin: 0.0px;float: none;" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/sns_album/i3/T1ulzWXotcXXb1upjX.jpg"/></span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><span style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; （注：阿里旺旺举证号提取方法，请参照：</span><span style="color: #000000;">怎么提取阿里旺旺举证号？</span><span style="color: #000000;">）</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#99ffff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>提问</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">我是阿里旺旺子帐号聊天的，怎么提供聊天记录举证号？</span></span></span></strong></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#ff99ff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>回答</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果您是子旺旺聊天的，请您用子旺旺提取聊天记录，并且反馈子账户会员名和子旺旺举证号。</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#99ffff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>提问</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">子账号（E客服）的会员名格式是什么样的？</span></span></span></strong></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#ff99ff" rowspan="3"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>回答</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 子账号会员名的格式形式如下：</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">主账号会员名+子账号昵称，中间用冒号隔开</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">例如：您的主账号会员名是&ldquo;淘宝&rdquo;，您的子账号可以是&ldquo;淘宝:小宝&rdquo;（主账号的会员名必须在前面，子账号的后缀可以自己取哦），这个&ldquo;淘宝:小宝&rdquo;就是您的子账号了。</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#99ffff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>提问</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">为什么完整填写订单信息后，点击保存后再提交，页面会一直显示没有保存成功无法提交呢？</span></span></span></strong></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#ff99ff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>回答</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 请查看是不是附件添加过大（单张图片不能超过3M）图片添加过多（最好不要超过3张），或更换浏览器（建议更换为火狐浏览器或谷歌）。</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#99ffff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>提问</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">为什么无法提交申诉？</span></span></span></strong></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#ff99ff" rowspan="4"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>回答</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可能有以下原因：</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">1.开放申诉入口的条件为：第一次提交后判定不成立的记录，从不成立那个时间段的14天之内（这里的14天也是基于评价还在受理时间的30天之内。如已超过30天无再次申诉入口，打个比方，如离受理时间还剩下6天，那么他如果去发起二次申诉的时间也只有6天）可以发起补充凭证的二次申诉</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">2.如果第一次提交后判定成立，此订单没有申诉入口。</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p style="margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">3.附件不是必写项，如果申诉时需要提供聊天记录，用举证号代替即可哦~</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#99ffff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>提问</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">为什么我第一次评价申诉失败后，就找不到第二次补充入口了呢？</span></span></span></strong></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#ff99ff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>回答</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 每个订单只有一次补充凭证的申诉机会，建议您准备好完整和充足的证据再做提交哦~</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#99ffff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>提问</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">为什么在提交申诉时，添加了附件，无法提交（页面不跳转）？</span></span></span></strong></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#ff99ff"><div align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;"><strong>回答</strong></span></span></span></div></td><td><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 14.0px;"><span style="font-family: simsun;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 附件只能是图片，先核实提交图片大小是否超过限制，不建议上传过多附件（如果是聊天记录，用举证号信息代替即可），或尝试更换浏览器或电脑进行重新添加（注：建议更换为火狐浏览器或谷歌）。</span></span></span></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><table border="1" bordercolor="#ffffff" width="740"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://bbs.taobao.com/catalog/thread/1338197-258751194.htm" target="_blank"><span style="font-size: 18.0px;"><span style="font-family: microsoft yahei;"><strong><span style="color: #3d85c6;">点此查看 更多【淘宝意见征集】</span></strong></span></span></a></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
